## v1.4.0 (2026-06-13)

**Changed by:** Salvage of closed PR #2318 — E501/format failures in newly-added test files on large feature PRs
**Verification:** verified-ci (ProjectHephaestus PR #1035)

### What changed

- Added Pattern F (E501 / ruff format failures in newly-added test files on a large multi-file feature PR).
- Added Quick Reference snippet for Pattern F: `pixi run ruff check hephaestus/ tests/` + `pixi run ruff format --check hephaestus/ tests/`.
- Documented two opposite E501 fix shapes: (F1) extract long literal to named constant; (F2) stop hand-wrapping calls that ruff format collapses.
- Added positive convention: `add_version_arg(parser)` helper + `@pytest.mark.parametrize("command,module_path,attr", ENTRY_POINTS)` integration test pattern for cross-cutting CLI flag rollouts.
